  "body": "### What is wrong?\r\n\r\nInstantiating a `ShardingVM` with a `CollationHeader` does not work, for multiple reasons:\r\n\r\n- it tries to build a `ShardingBlock` instead of a `Collation` from it\r\n- it tries to get transactions from the trie which fails with a `KeyError`, indicating some sort of bin/hex trie root problem (?)\r\n- potentially additional reasons",
